    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Ctenosciara cracens sp. n. (A – C paratypes, D, E holotype). A, B. Antennal flagellomere 4, lateral view. C. Apical part of front tibia, prolateral view. D. Part of hypopygium, ventral view. E. Gonostylus, ventral view. Scale 0.1 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/280644/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.280645>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Ctenosciara cracens sp. n. (paratypes). A. Part of hypopygium, ventral view. B – E. Gonostylus, ventral view. Scale 0.1 mm." ;
